</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_62" id="29v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, vesten Buscho,
                            <expan>burgr<ex>afen</ex></expan> czum Betlern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Buscho, uns ist fürgelegt worden, wie daz
                        ir den <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Weiszemburg<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>ern</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, <add>von</add>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nothafts <add>wegen</add>
<expan>gefange<ex>n</ex></expan> habt. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz
                        ir durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, ledig lassen wöllet,
                            <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> wir niht wissen, daz wir mit euch ichts
                        anders <expan>czeschicke<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> lieb und gut. Das
                            <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
